Android ListView with Rounded Corners and Highlighting I've just been asked for a helping hand about how to have a ListView with rounded corners, so here's the solution.
In Android it's fairly trivial to have a ListView with rounded corners on the first and last element. The problems comes when you want to be able to highlight the view, whether that be via press or with a focus.
The solution is nice and simple, the highlight applied by the system can be removed by setting the ListSelector color to transparent android:listSelector=&quot;#00000000&quot;

